Hit and miss

Excellent seafood! I ordered the Perfect Storm with a side of sausage, which was just thinly sliced kielbasa generously portioned. I just thought it would be something a little less generic. It was still great. You're there for the seafood, anyway. There are more than a few locations, so order online or stop in. As a food delivery rider, I can attest that they're always busy.
Food Was Very Good....
Addicted to the sweet potato fries
The service was great, my family enjoyed the food

Well I order my food through y Uber eat, I was exited to try it but I got so disappointed about how the chef made my food. He/she made it extremely salty that I wasn’t able to eat it, I ask for spicy not salty And I called the restaurant they told me that I have to contact Uber in order for them to make a replace dish until now Uber didn’t handle the issue, so I’m super disappointed to lose 50 something $ and not able to have a descent dish. I won’t use Uber eat anymore
Food is delicious... Great wings!
Took my girlfriend for dinner as my friend had recomended it. Wow the Juicy King Crab Special is amazing!!   Will definitely recommend to my friends to order here for dinner

My wife and I were craving a Real authentic seafood and kept looking until we stumbled on this gem.  The Juicy King Crab Special is amazing , very tasteful , fresh and not freezer burnt . The staff are very friendly .
The best seafood 🦀🦞🦐🦪🦀🍤
the food is excellent
I totally enjoy my order. The service was very good. My bag was still hot when I got home.
Great seafood and service ice
They are really good my 8 yr old loves them
Good food. Good service.
Great place! Their takeout was absolutely perfect!
Amazing seafood and super attentive takeout service. The Fried Shrimp Basket was fresh and yummy. Will clearly recommend this place to others.
Delicious! Loved the king crab and their sauce. I’d recommend to try many different items.
The seafood is deliciously delightful in taste. I had the king crab and was introduced to oysters for the first time here. You can taste the freshness.
Food was dee-lish!! We ordered shrimp, corn, broccoli and potatoes then ordered chicken tenders and calamari. My husband, our four year old son and myself LOVED it!!! We're definitely going back!!
Awesome seafood restaurant.  Excellent Juicy King Carb Special, Shrimp, fish & Oyster.
Food was tasty. 3 stars because they forgot my drink
This seafood restaurant is really a must-try! The Crab & Shrimp here are fantastic, and the service is really exceptional.
The King Crab was fresh as well. My husband love Crawfish. We ordered take-out and the food was still hot.
It was everything I wanted it to be in a seafood boil 😋 can't wait to go back
Excellent food.  I was impressed.  I would definitely eat there again🤗

The food here is flavorful. The first time I had their seafood boil, I knew it will never be my last. You have a range of sauces, spicy level, and seafood (whether that be crawfish, crab, clams, shrimps) to choose from. The staff is super sweet and catering. Delivery is also fast too!!! You will not regret it 🦐🦞🦀❤️

A very nice restaurant in the area! You will never be disappointed for sure. Their Juicy King Crab Special was very admirable and delicious. So for anyone looking for a restaurant in our new normal, this is a good place.
Super cheap with the portions (literally one corn and two small little potatoes in my boil) and the sauce was way tooo salty!
We ordered the Seafood Combo for 2 comprised of Juicy King Crab Special , Shrimp , Clam & Cajun Boil.  The service was exceptional, the interior clean, and the food was very good.

This is a perfect seafood restaurant! We have been lucky enough to order this restaurant over the month and must say this might be the best we have ever been to. Everything served was spectacular!!  ❤️
Takeout is amazing and the Juicy King Crab Special is so fresh.  It can get busy but they do have a great job.
Love their Fried Whiting Fish Basket & mussels. It's always good. So delicious!
We had drinks and seafood. The service was very good, lovely, friendly, polite staff, have been very helpful with all our requests. Juicy King Crab Special were very nice and food tasted good too.
Love it
Great seafood. Lots of options.

Had a great time for a birthday dinner, we ordered the 2 person seafood platter and added Fried Shrimp Basket . Everything was high quality, the Juicy King Crab Special made an impression on my 20 year old.
Best fried oysters I’ve had in the north. Great chicken tenders and shrimp too. Fries are great as well. All boxes checked & friendly service. Worth every trip!
Excellent seafood restaurant in the area! Last week, I thanked your staff for serving my takeout as fast as he could. I didn't regret my decision to order my dinner here for the first time.

My boyfriend and and I were looking for a restaurant to order this evening. The seafood was delicious and the takeout service was great. The waitress' recommendation was a great choice and we would order here again.
This will be a regular takeout place for us! Great customer service and the seafood comes in a very generous portion. LOVE. IT.
Excellent fresh seafood! King Crab and Chicken Wings all at peak freshness and flavor.
This restaurant offers fantastic takeout service and enjoyable seafood. My favourite place around NY. The Fried Shrimp Basket came out rapidly and the rates were affordable. Recommended.
The Juicy King Crab Special was tasty. We enjoyed every moment and we will definitely order other dishes. Recommended.
GREAT TAKEAWAY. The Fried Tilapia Baskets were tasty; can't go wrong with Chicken Wings & Shrimp and the Oysters were good. Very happy~
The seafood was fantastic. So addictive! Their service is very stunning! I liked it so much. I would have to recommend this place to everyone.

This seafood restaurant is really a must-try! The Crab & Shrimp here are fantastic, and the service is really exceptional. The overall experience is memorable, and I'm happy because these guys were able to satisfy my cravings. Very worth it!
It was nice I had a Dungeness crab and a pound of king crab with some sides
So delicious I'm going back today soon as they open.
Great food, reasonably priced and the customer service is excellent
Food was very tasty I paid for the eggs 🥚 please send them next time
The food is really great🤤I had their kring crab specialty and it is really worth it. Love the Cajun fries must try!!!!
Amazing juicy seafood for real. The sauces and seafood are fresh and flavorful.  I ordered delivery and everything arrived hot. Totally worth the price, I will for sure be a returning customer!! 🦀🦐🍤🌽
My new favorite place close to home

The food was so delicious. We ordered the Perfect Storm in garlic butter seasoning and it was great for 2 people, assuming you want to be stuffed. I almost wish they included more corns, because I could eat that all day; I kept going back in the bag for more sauce. Really happy this place opened near by as we will definitely be repeat customers.
Food was very tasty ! Definitely will return. Could’ve cooked a little longer since corn takes a while. Sauce was a bit salty at the end. But otherwise very very good.

Great food and service! We ordered 1lb of crab legs, 1lb mussels and 1lb clams tossed in the garlic butter sauce. We also tried the popcorn shrimp and hush puppies. All were super delish, will definitely be back.
Food was outstanding !! Service was awesome and they were super attentive. Seafood was fresh and flavorful. Will most definitelyyyyyy be going back !!
AMAZING FOOD !!! FAST SERVICE AND LOTS OF WELCOMING SERVICE
great customer service, food is phenomenal, and very affordable.
Great Food!!! Love it, will order it again.
